*
!.gitignore
!b
!b.yaml
!b.lock
# Vendor the argsh runtime (pure-bash, ~55KB) so `lo` — and crucially
# `lo doctor`, which diagnoses the rest of the toolchain — runs on a fresh
# clone before `b install`. Pinned to b.lock; `b install` refreshes it.
# NOT argsh.so (that's a platform-specific native binary — fetched by b).
!argsh